    "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/decision/vad-hemolysis-accepted-ar03",
    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/credibility-team-lead",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team concluded that the comprehensive literature review of 42 published studies, combined with Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification, provides sufficient evidence to accept the CFD hemolysis predictions for the VAD COU. The literature survey was judged to be a thorough and systematic evidence-gathering activity that adequately characterises model performance across the operating envelope. All 13 credibility factors were reviewed; while achieved levels are below required levels in most factors, the weight of published evidence was deemed to compensate for the absence of dedicated in-house experimental testing. Decision: Accepted.",
